OL,3,CIll health prompts NRW Chief's exit,
OL,4,Cafter seven years at the helm
OL,6,FThe Chief Executive of Natural
OL,7,FResources Wales (NRW) has announced
OL,8,Fshe will be stepping down from the
OL,9,Frole after seven years.
OL,11,FClare Pillman has held the #150,000 a
OL,12,Fyear role as the head of the
OL,13,Fenvironmental regulator since 2018,
OL,14,Falthough it is believed that she has
OL,15,Fbeen off sick for up to 6 months,
OL,16,Faccording to board papers.
OL,18,FMs Pillman has overseen the
OL,19,Forganisation during some significant
OL,20,Fmoments in recent years.
