OL,6,FIn February 2020, Wales saw the worst
OL,7,Fflooding on record. Storms Ciara and
OL,8,FDennis brought exceptional rainfall
OL,9,Fwhich saw widespread flooding and
OL,10,Fextensive damage to more than 3,000
OL,11,Fproperties.
OL,13,FA review into the flooding found that
OL,14,FNRW's operations had been stretched
OL,15,Fduring this time, hampering its
OL,16,Fability to react to "rapidly
OL,17,Fescalating and unforeseen events on
OL,18,Fthe ground".
