OL,6,FIt also found 12 flood warnings were
OL,7,Fnot issued when they should have been,
OL,8,Fand six were issued late.
OL,10,FThe organisation came under fire again
OL,11,Flast year when residents and
OL,12,Fpoliticians criticised NRW for not
OL,13,Fgiving as early warning as possible in
OL,14,Fthe build-up to Storm Bert which
OL,15,Fcaused devastation in parts of Wales
OL,16,Fin November.
OL,18,FAnd in July 2024, an Y Byd ar Bedwar
OL,19,Finvestigation saw whistleblowers speak
OL,20,Fout about "inaction and bureaucracy at
OL,21,Fthe organisation".
