OL,6,FAt that time Clare Pillman refused an
OL,7,Finterview request to respond to
OL,8,Fresearch that revealed NRW did not
OL,9,Fattend more than half of pollution
OL,10,Fincidents reported to them in 2023.
OL,12,FInstead in a statement, she said that
OL,13,Freal progress had been made in
OL,14,Fimproving the quality of water, land
OL,15,Fand air over the last 30 years.
OL,17,FIn November, NRW announced it was
OL,18,Fmaking #10 million worth of cuts,
OL,19,Fslashing nearly 250 jobs and ceasing
OL,20,Fthe operation of cafes and shops at
OL,21,Fits visitors centres.
