OL,3,CIll health prompts NRW Chief's exit,
OL,4,Cafter seven years at the helm
OL,6,FShe said: "I will always love the
OL,7,FWelsh environment - but the time is
OL,8,Fright now to hand NRW over. I have
OL,9,Freached, at 60, the age at which I
OL,10,Falways presumed I would move on...
OL,12,F"Deciding when to retire is never
OL,13,Feasy, but I can do so knowing that NRW
OL,14,Fwill continue its vital work. I have
OL,15,Fbeen so proud to work with expert,
OL,16,Fpassionate colleagues who give
OL,17,Feverything to serve the people and
OL,18,Fland of Wales."
