OL,6,FWhat does Natural Resources Wales do?
OL,7,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) is an
OL,8,Fenvironmental regulator responsible
OL,9,Ffor protecting the environment and
OL,10,Ftackling climate change.
OL,12,FIts responsibilities ranges from
OL,13,Fsustainable management of water
OL,14,Fresources, woodlands and fisheries to
OL,15,Fenvironment regulation across Wales.
OL,17,FOfficers are responsible for
OL,18,Fmonitoring flood risk, biodiversity,
OL,19,Fwater quality, as well as regulatory
OL,20,Fwork.
