OL,6,FLlyr Gruffydd, who chairs the Senedd's
OL,7,Fclimate committee, recently warned NRW
OL,8,Fhas been in a constant state of
OL,9,Fevolution and flux for many, many
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FAppearing before the committee for
OL,13,Fscrutiny of NRW's 2023/24 annual
OL,14,Freport in March, Sir David Henshaw who
OL,15,Fchairs the NRW board warned: "It's
OL,16,Fgoing to be a rough old 12 months or
OL,17,Fso."
